Missouri_City.KTXH: KTXH, virtual channel 20 (UHF digital channel 19), is a MyNetworkTV owned-and-operated television station licensed to Houston, Texas, United States. The station is owned by the Fox Television Stations subsidiary of 21st Century Fox, as part of a duopoly with Fox owned-and-operated station KRIV (channel 26). The two stations share studio facilities located on Southwest Freeway in Houston (between the Uptown and Greenway Plaza districts).
